{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, residue-level scoring profiles are defined by applying Y = exp(-X) to the m.s.e.",
    "reconstruction error at each position of the given sequence.",
    "All the performance metrics reported are computed by analysing 10,000 scored sequences for each database, except for the diverse datasets (Supplementary Table 5).",
    "For datasets smaller than 10,000, the whole dataset is used.",
    "Classification."
  ]
}